# On-Premises Role

## Architect

Responsável pelo design de arquiteturas de TI baseadas nas regras de negócio

- Enterprise or System Architect
    - Create Holistic IT Architecture Designs

- Application Architect
    - Design Applications

- Storage Architect
    - Design Storage Infrastructure

- Network Architect
    - Design Network Architecture

- Security Architect
    - Specity Security Requirements

## System Administrator

Responsável por instalar, dar surporte e manter computadores e servidores

- Hardware
    - Install/Repair/Replace/Maintain

- Computer Systems
    - Support/Maintain

- Hardware/Software
    - Monitor Pertormance

- Computer systems
    - Monitor Network

- Computer systems
    - Manage Log Files

- Computer Systems
    - Service Outage Response

- OSs and Applications
    - Instal/Update/ Patch

- File Systems
    - Manage

- Entire Environment
    - Back Up and Recover

- Users
    - Manage Users and ACcess Control

## Application Administrator

Mantem a aplicação da organização de pé e rodando

- Application
    - Install/Update/Tune

- Application
    - Diagnose/Troubleshoot

- Tuning and Troubleshooting
    - Collaborate with Development

- Application Integration
    - Collaborate with Technical Teams

- Application
    - Manage Documentation

- Application
    - Manage Logs

## Database Administrator

Instalam e mantem o ambiente do banco de dados
Promovem treinamento de como utilizar os bancos de dados

- Operations DBA
    - Manage Databases

- Development DBA
    - Design Database Architectures

- Data Administrator
    - Manage Data Access

## Network Administrator

Responsável por projetar, instalar, configurar e manter a rede local (LAN) e a rede de longa distância (WAN)

- Projetar
- Instalar/Configurar
- Manter
- Expandir

## Storage Administrator

Responsável pelo gerenciar o sistema de armazenamento

- Storage Systems
    - Instal/Configure/ Replace

- Storage Systems
    - Maintain/Test

- Storage Systems
    - Back up and Recover

- Storage Systems
    - Monitor Environment

- Storage
    - Manage Capacity

- Application
    - Collaborate with Technical Teams

## Security Administrator

Responsável por instalar, configurar, gerenciar, monitorar e impor as soluções de segurança

- IT Security
    - Analyze Requirements

- IT Security
    - Implement Security Policies

- IT Security
    - Defend Against Unauthorized Access

- IT Security
    - Monitor Network Traffic

- IT Security
    - Manage Support Tools

- IT Security
    - Perform Vulnerability Tests

- IT Security
    - Conduct Security Audits

- IT Security
    - Enforce Compliance

# Quiz

1 - Qual função de uma empresa on-premises é responsável por instalar, dar suporte e manter os computadores?

(x) System administrator
( ) Application administrator
( ) Storage administrator
( ) Database administrator

2 - Qual função de uma empresa on-premises é responsável pela defesa contra o acesso não autorizado?

( ) Application administrator
( ) Storage administrator
(x) Security administrator
( ) Database administrator